<h3>Web Stickers</h3>
<p> To show your support for the TV Parental Guidelines, please download the TV Parental Guidelines logo and place it on your organization’s website to encourage greater understanding of the TV ratings and controls. The logo should link back to the TVGuidelines.org website. <a href="images/stickers/TVGuidelinesStickers.zip" target="_blank">Click here</a> to download a zipped file containing the sticker in different colors. If you need additional sizes, please <a href="contactUs.html">contact us</a>.</p><br>

